{
  "stem": "888.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe the older people, you know, more grown up people who might have spoken Slavic, you understand, and spoke with these people from, you know, from the camps, and they would probably-- but you know, they tried to protect us in a sense, that it didn't come out to the younger people and tell you, you know.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we surmised, you know, that something, something is happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I mean, we never heard this, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, you know, we knew that there was quite a lot of killing going on in Poland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Polish Jews, you know, were killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You did know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, but---",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the specific-- because like I said, you know, people used to talk, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people, some people who ran away from Poland, you know, and told some people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it wasn't conversation which people, grown up people, would relate to, to smaller, smaller children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was 15.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just turned 15.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With Nachmen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nachmen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was older, two years older.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for some reason or other, he looked younger, you know, because he was a little sickly looking.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were moved to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we, we were put into a block over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was called-- you know, to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Barrack 39, I remember it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was-- 39, you know, sort of was kind of separated from the other barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because this was a transitional people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the people were sort of towards-- there was a small little-- like a-- little, not a hill, but sort of like a little higher up ground.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were the-- there was a lot of people, you know, who were there, regular people lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
